OL,3,CDoes the Polestar 4 offer a glimpse of
OL,4,Cthe cars of the future?
OL,6,FTechnology has become increasingly
OL,7,Fcentral to modern vehicles, with no
OL,8,Fmore striking example of this in 2024
OL,9,Fthan the Polestar 4, which does not
OL,10,Fhave a rear windscreen.
OL,12,FInstead, the electric car uses sensors
OL,13,Fand cameras to display a live feed on
OL,14,Fa display in the rear view mirror.
OL,16,FThe unique approach has helped
OL,17,FPolestar stand out, something chief
OL,18,Ftechnology officer Lutz Stiegler said
OL,19,Fis important to the company.
