OL,3,CDoes the Polestar 4 offer a glimpse of
OL,4,Cthe cars of the future?
OL,6,FHe said the firm wanted to create a
OL,7,F"different environment" inside the
OL,8,Fcar, as well as offering a "different
OL,9,Fsilhouette" from other vehicles.
OL,11,F"What really drove us into this is the
OL,12,Foverall concept optimisation of the
OL,13,Fentire car ` we wanted to have a car
OL,14,Fthat is aerodynamically efficient, and
OL,15,Fthat requires getting the rear end of
OL,16,Fthe roof down," he told the PA news
OL,17,Fagency.
