OL,6,F"With this, you get a very narrow
OL,7,Fspace for the rear windscreen, and
OL,8,Fthat actually doesn't give enough or
OL,9,Fsufficient visibility... and with the
OL,10,Frear seats we are more comfort-
OL,11,Forientated anyway, with a very relaxed
OL,12,Fposition.
OL,14,F"We wanted to create a different
OL,15,Fenvironment, and I think many will
OL,16,Flike it; others will hate it because
OL,17,Fthey want to see something when they
OL,18,Flook in the mirror.
