OL,6,F"My experience is it takes a few days,
OL,7,Fbut then you don't see the difference
OL,8,Fany longer, and then it's only a
OL,9,Fpositive.
OL,11,F"But of course, for us, it was a tool
OL,12,Fto do two things ` one is getting the
OL,13,Frear roof down, and by that creating a
OL,14,Fdifferent silhouette of the car than
OL,15,Fwe would have with a rear window, and
OL,16,Fthe other is getting some attractive
OL,17,Ftechnology in the car."
