OL,3,CDoes the Polestar 4 offer a glimpse of
OL,4,Cthe cars of the future?
OL,6,FLike many modern cars, Polestar's
OL,7,Felectric vehicles come with a central
OL,8,Ftouchscreen console from which all
OL,9,Felements of the car's interior and
OL,10,Fexterior can be adjusted.
OL,12,FThis system also includes a special
OL,13,Fversion of Google Maps specifically
OL,14,Fdesigned for electric vehicles, where
OL,15,Froute planning takes into account the
OL,16,Fcar's current level of charge, the
OL,17,Fnumber of recharging stops a driver
OL,18,Fmay want to make, and how much battery
OL,19,Flife the driver would like to arrive
OL,20,Fat their destination with.
