OL,3,CDoes the Polestar 4 offer a glimpse of
OL,4,Cthe cars of the future?
OL,6,FThe array of in-car sensors can also
OL,7,Fmonitor the driver's fatigue levels
OL,8,Fand even where their eyes are looking
OL,9,F` giving them a nudge if they drift
OL,10,Ffrom the road or appear to be getting
OL,11,Fweary.
OL,13,FIndividual drivers can also create
OL,14,Fpersonal profiles that arrange the
OL,15,Fcentral display and seat settings to
OL,16,Ftheir personal layout and preference `
OL,17,Fin much the same way different Netflix
OL,18,Fprofiles on a single account would
OL,19,Fwithin one household.
