OL,3,CDoes the Polestar 4 offer a glimpse of
OL,4,Cthe cars of the future?
OL,6,FIt is a further sign that modern cars
OL,7,Fare becoming more of an extension of
OL,8,Four already digital-centric lives.
OL,10,FMr Stiegler told PA that Polestar
OL,11,Fwanted to "focus our money on things
OL,12,F(technology) that really make a
OL,13,Fdifference", including "infotainment"
OL,14,Fsystems and continuing the company's
OL,15,Fcollaboration with Google.
OL,17,FHe added that using technology to fine-
OL,18,Ftune the performance of its cars is
OL,19,Fsomething it is passionate about.
