OL,3,CDoes the Polestar 4 offer a glimpse of
OL,4,Cthe cars of the future?
OL,6,F"The drivability of the car is also
OL,7,Fimportant because most of our
OL,8,Fcustomers are coming from the Polestar
OL,9,F2 and want to have that special
OL,10,Fdriving feeling that a Polestar has,
OL,11,Fwith the quite firm suspension,
OL,12,Fresponse on the accelerator pedal and
OL,13,Fbrake, and that, of course, requires a
OL,14,Flot of tuning to do, and we also have
OL,15,Fa lot of software involvements that we
OL,16,Fhave to do," he said.
OL,18,F"So, from that perspective, of course,
OL,19,FR&D (research and development) is
OL,20,Fextremely important."
