OL,3,CDoes the Polestar 4 offer a glimpse of
OL,4,Cthe cars of the future?
OL,6,FThe EV maker also plans to build a car
OL,7,Fmade from bonded aluminium, making it
OL,8,Flighter, and involving fewer rivets
OL,9,Fand mixed metal structures.
OL,11,FMr Stiegler added that Polestar is the
OL,12,Ffirst to master this kind of
OL,13,Fproduction capable of running at mass
OL,14,Flevel, and that the end result will be
OL,15,F"highly technological".
